# Ignore everything
*

# Keep
!.gitignore
!CMakeLists.txt
!src/
!src/**
!test/
!test/**
!benchmarks/
!benchmarks/**
!bench_output/
!bench_output/**
!meta/
!engine/
!engine/**
!stored_engines/
!stored_engines/**
!uci/
!uci/**

# Ignore build directories anywhere
**/build/
**/debug/
**/release/
**/x64/
**/x86/

# Ignore CMake generated files
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
*.cmake
Makefile
*.vcxproj
*.vcxproj.filters
*.vcxproj.user
*.sln

# Ignore compiled binaries and libraries
*.exe
# But keep stored engines
!stored_engines/**.exe
!meta/**
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.a
*.lib
*.o
*.obj

# Ignore IDE specific files
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Ignore OS specific files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Ignore testing artifacts
Testing/
test/chess_tests